@dev Calculate the total value of assets held by the Vault and all
      strategies and update the supply of USDs.

@dev Internal to calculate total value of all assets held in Vault.
 @return value in ETH (1e18)

@dev Internal to calculate total value of all assets held in Strategies.
 @return value in ETH (1e18)

returns._0: uint256 Balance of asset in decimals of asset

isOwner().details: Returns true if the caller is the current owner.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

rebase().details: Calculate the total value of assets held by the Vault and all      strategies and update the supply of USDs.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

totalValue().details: Determine the total value of assets held by the vault and its         strategies.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

checkBalance(address).notice: Get the balance of an asset held in Vault and all strategies.
